I'll leave the rest of your post alone, since there may be valid points about lower end monks getting the shaft, but....<br>
<br>
Sk/Pal/Rng spells do NOT add alot of power to our class.  Its debatable how much power they do add since most of our spells tend to be pretty useless.  Knights specifically are meant to be defensive classes and we give up alot of damage power to be so(at least compared to monk/rogue).<br>
<br>
That all important taunt button you mention for warriors is also pretty much marginal at best for its worth.  The taunt button has never been very effective.  Thats a big part of the reason they added rage proc weapons.<br>
<br>
As far as having piles of gear with AC and HP, pretty much every class gets that nowadays.  Thats how we got into this problem in the first place.<br>
<br>
Monks can easily break 6k hp now.  Hell even casters can break 5k.<br>
